Group.Name: Cloud Settings
Group.Description: Settings for Google App Engine connection

Prop.Name: Project Id
Prop.Description: Project Id as specified in Google Clout Platform site.

Prop.Name: Application Version
Prop.Description: Contains the version identifier for the latest version of the app's code. May only contain lowercase letters, digits, and hyphens. Must begin and end with a letter or digit. Must not exceed 63 characters.
